data.description:
$18,668 below tax appraised value in Canyon ISD. Pinnacle Intermediate school. This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem boasts two spacious living areas, a cozy fireplace, and a dining area seamlessly connected to the well-appointed kitchen. 3 bedrooms downstairs 1 bedroom uptairs.

Nestled on a large corner lot, the property features beautiful trees, a convenient storage building, and a generous utility room with a pantry. The primary bedroom offers the luxury of two closets.

Make this lovely, spacious home yours today, and enjoy the comfort and convenience it provides.
